<P>ANECDOTES
OF
PAINTING in ENGLAND;
With &s;ome Account of the principal Arti&s;ts;
And incidental NOTES on other ARTS;
Collected by the late
Mr. GEORGE VERTUE;
And now dige&s;ted and publi&s;hed from his original MSS.
By Mr. HORACE WALPOLE.
The SECOND EDITION.
<HI>Multa rena&s;centur quae jam cecidere.</HI></P>
<P>VOL. I.</P>
<P>Printed by THOMAS KIRGATE at STRAWBERRY-HILL,
MDCCLXV.</P>
